>> title: Industry Sour (Alternative Recipe)
>> tags: gin,coupe,shaken

Chill a #coupe{} in the freezer.

Fill a #cocktail shaker{} with @ice{}.

Add @lemon juice{1%oz}, @Drambuie{1%oz}, @Cynar{1%oz}, and @absinthe or pastis{2%shakes}.

Shake for at least 30 seconds.

Serve in #coupe{}, garnish with @lemon twist{1}.